== designation1 ==
=== National Historic site ===
* Terado Ōtsuka Kofun: Designated a National Historic site in 2015 as part of the Otokuni Kofun Cluster.<ref>Ministry of Education, Culture, Sports, Science and Technology Notification No. 38, March 10, 2015</ref>
* Otokuni Kofun Cluster: Expanded in 2016 to include additional Kofuns, with the name changed to Otokuni Kofun Cluster.<ref>Ministry of Education, Culture, Sports, Science and Technology Notification No. 31, March 1, 2016</ref><ref>[http://www.bunka.go.jp/koho_hodo_oshirase/hodohappyo/2015112003.html "Regarding the designation1 of Historic sites, etc."] (Agency for Cultural Affairs, November 20, 2015)</ref>
